# Copy this file to `.dev.vars` and fill in the values for local development
# with `wrangler pages dev`. `.dev.vars` is gitignored — never commit a real key.
#
# Production secrets are set separately via:
#   wrangler pages secret put ANTHROPIC_API_KEY --project-name borbala-portfolio
# or in the Cloudflare dashboard.

ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=""
